    "asOf": "2005-07-26",
    "date": "2005-09-07T20:19:34Z",
    "text": "Cures Can Be Found Act of 2005 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow tax credits for donations: (1) to stem cell research or storage facilities; (2) of umbilical cord blood. Allows credits only for donations to facilities that do not engage in research on stem cells derived from human embryos.\n\nAllows a business tax credit for stem cell research and storage expenses."
